{"tid":1603251,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有無可能申請禁制令禁制無number警員執法?","createTime":"2019-09-29T15:44:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T15:37:44.000Z","uid":46578,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"b780274d0eb17d0e15a7936e60fc0fa5e76da354","tid":1603251,"uid":46578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:44:38.000Z","msg":"而家大部分警渣垃圾做野時,無number無樣完全不能被監察.<br />\n但根據警例佢地係一定要出示委任證同numbernumber, 本身佢自認無number時都已經犯例. 但要告佢真係難個登天. <br />\n但若果申請到禁制令,情況就可能唔同. 一方面可以大家都多個盾, 另一方面亦真正可以彰顯法治未死."},{"pid":"d737f51529dff796abe06b9dc8d318045b804670","tid":1603251,"uid":46578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:49:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53f03515ebf4c8e1373124a5d65357e67677cbd6","tid":1603251,"uid":193032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:50:41.000Z","msg":"推到有法律巴絲答"},{"pid":"e2e9b4dd974d93857a00a9ef2d865e971433ddcf","tid":1603251,"uid":191446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:55:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"322d63ebfa28c633c85734554c2ede6e4b9b0d98","tid":1603251,"uid":46578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:03:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7364cb2410ac97179d1d0d23f7318787e2c6748","tid":1603251,"uid":19421,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:15:56.000Z","msg":"有撚用咩 你諗下禁制令邊個負責實行？"},{"pid":"93650904bdae62a7d770f8e08a3065961db3e1f4","tid":1603251,"uid":93311,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:18:48.000Z","msg":"無 因為依家係人治"},{"pid":"c7d1a125f1b9be824f6c16425c87baf5d76bbfa3","tid":1603251,"uid":46578,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"b7364cb2410ac97179d1d0d23f7318787e2c6748","tid":1603251,"uid":19421,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:15:56.000Z","msg":"有撚用咩 你諗下禁制令邊個負責實行？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:23:26.000Z","msg":"係同邊個執行係無闗<br />\n只要有禁制令<br />\n警渣若果直接違反 係直接刑事 法庭可以直接落Charge 唔駛警渣做野<br />\n而且唔係一條罪咁簡單<br />\n係可以連埋公職人員行為失當一齊告<br />\n到時佢地一定要縮<br />\n<br />\n又若果係政府口中所謂法治<br />\n係無理由唔批<br />\n<br />\n1, 警例寫到明要有Number有委任證先可以執法<br />\n2, 若果警例只係for reference only  咁就真係人治<br />\n<br />\n不過我想要有再有力條例去申請"},{"pid":"07c05ab22fd466856d4e59c4c9868ac44b70012a","tid":1603251,"uid":77740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:26:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e007d4a3ae2a6ce38b9b3c1882065f7f5993dddb","tid":1603251,"uid":54014,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b7364cb2410ac97179d1d0d23f7318787e2c6748","tid":1603251,"uid":19421,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:15:56.000Z","msg":"有撚用咩 你諗下禁制令邊個負責實行？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T19:13:25.000Z","msg":"執達吏，就算真係唔show委任證，至少都可以拉埋法庭啲人出黎食煙。"},{"pid":"50cc751486ecd94b078fcae58e608dbba9766b78","tid":1603251,"uid":145296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b7364cb2410ac97179d1d0d23f7318787e2c6748","tid":1603251,"uid":19421,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:15:56.000Z","msg":"有撚用咩 你諗下禁制令邊個負責實行？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T19:14:30.000Z","msg":"冇用架<br />\n但係政治現實就係乜都要試"},{"pid":"c66b607f1863e23248fda073508c5685d4b9ab53","tid":1603251,"uid":280136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T19:15:31.000Z","msg":"［手足入］希望大家可以多D留意屋企樓下E個位，提防D奇怪人搵有用垃圾<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1603671\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1603671</a>"},{"pid":"15637575600a179a1a4dc664668d054ba8c45ced","tid":1603251,"uid":46578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T00:30:22.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"fd20a9e6a28f59ad022d9991e320eb59dccf09ab","tid":1603251,"uid":43067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T00:3